531215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Aug 05, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104qdt1665702815241.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdt1665702815241.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/qdt1665702815241.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"qdt1665702815241\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Font Set Section\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">The font section defines information about characters in meta character sets. It is used to map the device definitions to Uniface features.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__topic_d63740e1_d63741e1_d63742e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63743e1_d63744e1_d63745e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">begin_font</code>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63746e1_d63747e1_d63748e1\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Font0Character</var>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">DeviceCharacterSequence</var> {<var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>}</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63749e1_d63750e1_d63751e1\">...</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63752e1_d63753e1_d63754e1\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">end_font</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__section_f11_f5h_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d678546e84\">Delimiters</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__1\">Mnemonic </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__2\">Explanation </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">begin_font</code>\n</p>\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">Number</var>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__2\">Mark start of font definition. </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\"><code class=\"ph codeph\">end_font</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"qdt1665702815241__table_d5558e1_d5559e1_d5560e1__entry__2\">Mark end of font definition. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__section_dwn_g5h_hcc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d678546e146\">Arguments</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__ul_d3r_g5h_hcc\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__li_d27800e1_d27801e1_d27802e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">MetaSetNumber</var>—meta character\n               set number; 0 through 7; see <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aud1665702670477.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aud1665702670477.html\" title=\"Meta character sets are used for translating installable character sets and defining translation tables. In earlier versions of Uniface, meta character sets were used as internal character sets instead of Unicode.\">Meta Character Sets</a>. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__li_d27803e1_d27804e1_d27805e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Font0Character</var>—character from\n               the <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owj1665702979491.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owj1665702979491.html\">Font 0 Meta Character Set</a>. This may be either the character or the\n               decimal value (^<var class=\"keyword varname\">nnn</var>) from the ‘KB’ or ‘Dec’ columns. </li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__li_d27806e1_d27807e1_d27808e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">DeviceCharacterSequence</var>—character definition in the form: <p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63761e1_d63762e1_d63763e1\">{<var class=\"keyword varname\">MetaSetNumber</var>\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">.</code>}<var class=\"keyword varname\">Character</var>\n</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63764e1_d63765e1_d63766e1\">If <var class=\"keyword varname\">MetaSetNumber</var> is omitted,\n                  character set 0 is assumed.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__li_d27809e1_d27810e1_d27811e1\"><var class=\"keyword varname\">Description</var>—optional\n               description or comments. They are often used to record the hexadecimal value and the\n               appearance (view) of the character. </li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__p_d63767e1_d63768e1_d63769e1\">The following definitions come from the P_SCREEN\n            device table:</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"qdt1665702815241__pre_tsz_h5h_hcc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">^BEGIN_FONT 0\n^^Fchar Dev_char(s) Hexa_decimal view Uniface Font_description\n^SP ^SP 20 \n! ! 21 ! \n\" \" 22 \" \n# # 23 # \n$ $ 24 $ \n% % 25 % \n ^^ ... snip\n0 0 30 0 \n1 1 31 1 \n2 2 32 2 \n3 3 33 3 \n ^^ ... snip\nv v 76 v \nw w 77 w \nx x 78 x \ny y 79 y \nz z 7A z \n{ { 7B { \n| | 7C | \n} } 7D } \n~ ~ 7E ~ \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 1\n^SP ^SP 20 \n&amp; | 7C ¦ \n- - 2D \n/ - 2D ¯ \n8 , 2C ¸ \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 2\n^SP ^SP 20 \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 3\n^SP ^SP 20 \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 4\n^^Fchar Dev_char(s) Hexa_decimal view Uniface Font_description\n^SP ^SP 20 \nA A 41 Α \nB B 42 Β \nE E 45 Ε \nF Z 5A Ζ \nG H 48 Η \nI I 49 Ι \nJ K 4B Κ \nL M 4D Μ \nM N 4E Ν \nO O 4F Ο \nQ P 50 Ρ \nS T 54 Τ \nV X 58 Χ \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 5\n^SP ^SP 20 \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 6\n^SP ^SP 20 \n^END_FONT\n^BEGIN_FONT 7\n^SP ^SP 20 \n~ ^SP 20 \n^END_FONT\n</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2531215\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Font Set Section Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Aug 05, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Font Set Section The font section defines information about characters in meta character sets. It is used to map the device definitions to Uniface features. begin_font Number Font0Character DeviceCharacterSequence { Description } ... end_font Delimiters Mnemonic Explanation begin_font Number Mark start of font definition. end_font Mark end of font definition. Arguments MetaSetNumber —meta character set number; 0 through 7; see Meta Character Sets . Font0Character —character from the Font 0 Meta Character Set . This may be either the character or the decimal value (^ nnn ) from the ‘KB’ or ‘Dec’ columns. DeviceCharacterSequence —character definition in the form: { MetaSetNumber . } Character If MetaSetNumber is omitted, character set 0 is assumed. Description —optional description or comments. They are often used to record the hexadecimal value and the appearance (view) of the character. The following definitions come from the P_SCREEN device table: ^BEGIN_FONT 0 ^^Fchar Dev_char(s) Hexa_decimal view Uniface Font_description ^SP ^SP 20 ! ! 21 ! \" \" 22 \" # # 23 # $ $ 24 $ % % 25 % ^^ ... snip 0 0 30 0 1 1 31 1 2 2 32 2 3 3 33 3 ^^ ... snip v v 76 v w w 77 w x x 78 x y y 79 y z z 7A z { { 7B { | | 7C | } } 7D } ~ ~ 7E ~ ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 1 ^SP ^SP 20 & | 7C ¦ - - 2D / - 2D ¯ 8 , 2C ¸ ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 2 ^SP ^SP 20 ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 3 ^SP ^SP 20 ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 4 ^^Fchar Dev_char(s) Hexa_decimal view Uniface Font_description ^SP ^SP 20 A A 41 Α B B 42 Β E E 45 Ε F Z 5A Ζ G H 48 Η I I 49 Ι J K 4B Κ L M 4D Μ M N 4E Ν O O 4F Ο Q P 50 Ρ S T 54 Τ V X 58 Χ ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 5 ^SP ^SP 20 ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 6 ^SP ^SP 20 ^END_FONT ^BEGIN_FONT 7 ^SP ^SP 20 ~ ^SP 20 ^END_FONT Copy Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}